Current target: ${t.sha256_now}
Recorded restored target: ${t.recorded_restored_sha256}

Checks:
${(lastRollbackPreview.checks||[]).map(c=>`${c.status.toUpperCase()} — ${c.id}: ${c.message} ${c.detail||''}`).join('\n')}

