Preview set target: ${s.preview_set_target}
Continuity handoff target: ${s.continuity_handoff_target}

Blockers:
${(d.blockers||[]).length ? (d.blockers||[]).map(b=>`${b.id}: ${b.message}`).join('\n') : 'None.'}

Written files:
${(d.written_files||[]).join('\n')||'None.'}

Created dirs:
